{"tid":1829040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚] 1.19 天下制裁  一齊做操紙師","createTime":"2020-01-18T11:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T16:56:17.000Z","uid":114580,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"ad1cc3697a1bd244c307d2c35e89ec36200e945a","tid":1829040,"uid":114580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"[拋磚] 1.19 天下制裁&nbsp; 一齊做操紙師<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1udafmc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1udafmc.png&h=2c9e7d80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「代友出」<br />\n有外媒表示(twitter見到，唔記得save低)香港人遊行比較少個人標語，次次都係拎蘋果同大紀元，分唔到主題同邊日打邊日，要搶佔外媒版面同引人訪問你，請自製標語，唔好等人派等人餵。<br />\n<br />\n自製標語唔需要靚，a2 紙皮side pen / 白板 己經足夠，feel到真誠同怒火，遊完行擦左佢/交俾紙皮婆婆，棄裝冇難度。<br />\n<br />\n寫得好，唔單止正規新聞會轉載，仲可以進攻meme page<br />\n<br />\n01 完美示範&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nEKD8Gm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnEKD8Gm.jpg&h=1f032c32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n02<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qyBK4e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqyBK4e0.png&h=b9329a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以下係一d潛力圖，改幾隻字就得:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QXpdc8v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQXpdc8v.jpg&h=bd725bcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nwe will not take this kneeling down / bend the knee? We don&rsquo;t kneel / Kneel? we don&rsquo;t do that here / Never compromise<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/18/191707_1c8fec8efd2e9edf581a09e87546bb13.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F18%2F191707_1c8fec8efd2e9edf581a09e87546bb13.jpeg&h=6b0c1d50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAt least Chancellor Palpatine was democratically elected<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xFPs119.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxFPs119.png&h=933f44fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nthe fascists and the furious 唔使改<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zebi8Hi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZebi8Hi.jpg&h=8d644efa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老人家0岩用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jKjXEPu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjKjXEPu.png&h=c2e46d12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔使改，好似有手足舉過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/szuQfnw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FszuQfnw.jpg&h=a80f7a6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCCP/carrie lam/hk govt gave me ptsd/depression<br />\nccp will call it separaist<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gQ6rx9H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgQ6rx9H.jpg&h=a89c6dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n寫乜好？<br />\n<br />\n1. Let hk be hk<br />\n2. I hate ccp more than i hate crowds&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n3. status quo is the problem<br />\n4. Better pissed off than pissed on<br />\n5. the most potent weapon of control for the oppressor is the mind of the oppressed<br />\n6. there's no end to the cruelty of ccp<br />\n7. This is not ok, boomer<br />\n8. 華風之弊，八字盡之：始於作偽，終於無恥 (嚴復)<br />\n9. the law is an ass - Charles Dickens<br />\n10. Every Lie you Tell Incurs a Debt to the Truth, Sooner or later that debt is paid<br />\n11. When you tear out a man's tongue, you're only telling the world that you fear what he might say.<br />\n<br />\n12. Carrie Lam was elected by only 777 cunts<br />\n13. Some people prefer dignity over money /&nbsp; Fabricated GDP<br />\n14. #AnywhereButChina<br />\n15. Hear hong kong now or be hong kong soon<br />\n16. Join the unions, fuck the government<br />\n17. Only justice will bring peace<br />\n<br />\nAnti CCP:<br />\n18. 習近平 小學生 唔識字 正文盲<br />\n19. 巨嬰國杯葛全世界<br />\n20. plague inc easy mode: wuhan pneumonia<br />\n21. 4 sinkholes in 6 weeks and you tell me to trust CCP<br 